Jules de Jongh https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jules_de_Jongh 0 Jules de Jongh (also incorrectly known as Jules Dejongh) is a British - American actress, voice actress, singer and television and radio presenter. She is known as the original English dub voices of Yugo and Evangelyne, on the show, Wakfu: The Animated Series for the first 2 seasons, the voice of Faith, the protagonist of the video game, Mirror's Edge and for the voice of Emily in the US version and others are Mavis (2009–12) and Rosie (2010–12) of Thomas Friends. She also voiced Skunk, the protagonist from the Irish animated series Skunk Fu!.
